Output out/amber-help.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1100
Set Height 760
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 30
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "export PS1='> '"
Enter
Type "export RUST_LOG=error"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "amber --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s
